metadata.name: Vie
metadata.description:
Vie
Height: 149.5
Occupation: Unemployed (gamer)
She plays games all the time without working because her family is wealthy.
She has a complex about her odd eyes and usually wears color contacts to hide them.
Loa once saw her naked eye, but she behaved as usual, so she only opens her heart to Loa.
